<h3 id="주요-저작-1">주요 저작<a role="anchor" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" data-no-popover="true" href="#주요-저작-1" class="internal"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="../../../도승지/철학/카뮈/이방인" class="internal alias" data-slug="도승지/철학/카뮈/이방인">이방인</a> - 부조리한 인간의 초상</li>
<li><a href="../../../도승지/철학/카뮈/시지프-신화" class="internal alias" data-slug="도승지/철학/카뮈/시지프-신화">시지프 신화</a> - 부조리에 관한 시론</li>
<li><a href="../../../도승지/철학/카뮈/페스트" class="internal alias" data-slug="도승지/철학/카뮈/페스트">페스트</a> - 연대를 통한 반항</li>
